Precipie

United States vs Henry Fitch

Precipie— In the Gen1 Court—

Michigan Territory-—ss—

The United States of America vs Henry Fitch of the District of Detroit, Trader— In debt for 400 dollars penalty for breach of the revenue law— Damage 1,00 dol. Bail required—

Mr Audrain Clerk

Sir.

Please to issue the above writ retle to the next Superior Court—

Sol. Sibley Atty for U. States by

special appointed of the

August 9. 1805— Colr of Detroit Distr

[In the handwriting of Solomon Sibley]
